      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:50:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团拒绝进一步谈判，必和必拓放弃 490 亿美元收购要约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bhp-abandons-49-billion-bid-after-anglo-holds-firm-on-rejection</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团决定不向英美资源集团提出确定的报价，而是暂时放弃这笔原本可能成为十多年来最大矿业交易的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/bhp-abandons-49-billion-bid-after-anglo-holds-firm-on-rejection</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 15:18:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>1980 年以来最严重冬季即将来临，阿根廷面临供暖危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/argentina-faces-natural-gas-crunch-with-colder-winter-setting-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着南半球冬季来临，气温低于预期，家庭供暖需求增加，阿根廷正在努力确保燃料供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/argentina-faces-natural-gas-crunch-with-colder-winter-setting-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:09:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FDIC 称美国银行部分证券的账面损失上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/us-banks-paper-losses-on-some-securities-increased-fdic-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦存款保险公司称，由于房地产市场进一步紧张，美国银行持有的两种主要证券的账面损失上季度进一步加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/us-banks-paper-losses-on-some-securities-increased-fdic-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 14:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金重返债券交易，过去经历波折</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/hedge-funds-return-to-convertible-bond-trade-with-chequered-past</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一种到期可转换为股票的债券发行量激增，有助于恢复在金融危机期间遭受重创的对冲基金策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/hedge-funds-return-to-convertible-bond-trade-with-chequered-past</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 10:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
